  "texts": [
    "The crystal had a cylindrical shape with a diameter of 3 inches and a height of 7 inches.",
    "It was enveloped in 2-3 mm of PTFE, enclosed by 2 mm of aluminum, and fitted with a quartz window.",
    "It featured a 3-inch PMT identical to those used in COSINE-100.",
    "The crystal was further shielded using 5-cm-thick lead bricks and installed at the IBS HQ ground laboratory in Daejeon, Korea.",
    "The DAQ system for this crystal also included a pre-amplifier, an ADC module, and a TCB, all with the same specifications as those in COSINE-100."
  ],
